== Submission Details

Paper submissions must be made through: [https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=cpsda2016 easychair.org].
Each submission is required to be in PDF format, and no more than *\<font color=red\>6 pages\<\/font\>* (including the abstract, figures, tables, and references) in a double column format.


